{
  "text": "Because of the predicted attractive properties of MDM waveguides, people have started to explore such structures experimentally. In particular, Dionne et al. [CITATION_1] have recently demonstrated waveguiding in a quasi-two-dimensional MDM geometry experimentally, showing clear evidence of a subwavelength guided mode with substantial propagation distances. With this as a background, it is important to explore the coupling of a dielectric slab waveguide into such a quasi-two-dimensional MDM geometry.",
